nG|---------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------|\r\nA|3--------------------------|\r\nE|------------------3------0-|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  Like no one's ever been here\r\nG|---------------|\r\nD|---------------|\r\nA|---------------|\r\nE|-------5-------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  Before or at all\r\nG|-----------------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------------|\r\nA|3----------------------------------|\r\nE|--------------3----------------0---|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  And don't you mention all the inches\r\nG|--------------------------------|\r\nD|--------------------------------|\r\nA|--------------------------------|\r\nE|----------5---------------------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  That are scraped on the doorframe\r\nG|-----------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------|\r\nA|3----------------------|\r\nE|-------3------------0--|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  We all know you tiptoed\r\nG|--------------------|----------------|\r\nD|--------------------|----------------|\r\nA|--------------------|3---------------|\r\nE|---------5----------|----------------|\r\n  Up to 4'1 back in '08[/tab]\r\n\r\n[Chorus]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|---------------------------------------|\r\nD|---------------------------------------|\r\nA|3--------------------------------------|\r\nE|----------------------0-------------5--|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  If you could see 'em now, you'd be proud\r\nG|-----------------------------|\r\nD|-----------------------------|\r\nA|-----------------------------|\r\nE|----------3------------------|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  But you'd think they's yuppies\r\nG|-------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------|\r\nA|3------------------------|\r\nE|-------------0----------5|[/tab]\r\n[tab]  Your funeral was beautiful\r\nG|-------------------------|\r\nD|-------------------------|\r\nA|-------------------------|\r\nE|----------3--------------|\r\n  I bet God heard you coming[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab]G|----------------|----------------|----------------|----------------|\r\nD|----------------|-----